AUTH
POST /api/auth/register → register
POST /api/auth/login → login
PUT /api/auth/profile → update profile
GET /api/auth → all authors
GET /api/auth/{id} → author by id

USER
GET /api/users/me → my profile
PUT /api/users/me → update my profile

ROLES
GET /api/roles → all roles
POST /api/admin/roles → create role (static)

ADMIN USERS
GET /api/admin/users → all users
GET /api/admin/users/{id} → user by id
PUT /api/admin/users/{id}/role → change role
DELETE /api/admin/users/{id} → delete user

AUTHORS (ADMIN)
POST /api/admin/users → create author
PUT /api/admin/users/{id} → update author

BOOKS
POST /api/books → create book
PUT /api/books/{id} → update book
DELETE /api/books/{id} → delete book
GET /api/books/{id} → book by id
GET /api/books → all books
GET /api/books/search?q= → search
GET /api/books/by-author/{id} → by author
GET /api/books/top-rated → top rated
GET /api/books/latest → latest

BOOK STATUS (ADMIN)
PUT /api/admin/books/{id}/status?active=true|false

CART
POST /api/cart/add → add item
GET /api/cart → view cart
PUT /api/cart/update → update qty
DELETE /api/cart/remove/{bookId} → remove item
DELETE /api/cart/clear → clear cart

WISHLIST
POST /api/wishlist/add/{bookId} → add
GET /api/wishlist → my wishlist
DELETE /api/wishlist/remove/{bookId} → remove

ORDERS
POST /api/orders/place → place order
GET /api/orders/my → my orders
GET /api/orders/{id} → order by id

ADMIN ORDERS
GET /api/admin/orders → all orders
PUT /api/admin/orders/{id}/status?status=

PAYMENT
POST /api/payments/initiate → initiate
POST /api/payments/verify → verify

SYSTEM
GET /api/config → config
GET /api/health → health